bug.short_desc: File conflict between kde-l10n-sr and other kde packages

long_desc.thetext:
On Fedora-Workstation-netinst-x86_64-24_Alpha-1.7.iso:
[mfabian@Fedora-Workstation-netinst-x86_6 ~]$ sudo dnf groupinstall kde-desktop-environment <-netinst-x86_6 ~]$ sudo dnf groupinstall kde-desktop-environment
[...]
エラー: トランザクションの確認時にエラー: file /usr/share/locale/sr@ijekavian/LC_MESSAGES/kfilemetadata.mo conflicts between attempted installs of kde-l10n-sr-15.12.3-3.fc24.noarch and kf5-kfilemetadata-5.20.0-1.fc24.x86_64 file /usr/share/locale/sr@ijekavianlatin/LC_MESSAGES/kfilemetadata.mo conflicts between attempted installs of kde-l10n-sr-15.12.3-3.fc24.noarch and kf5-kfilemetadata-5.20.0-1.fc24.x86_64
[...]
file /usr/share/locale/sr@latin/LC_MESSAGES/baloo_file_extractor.mo conflicts between attempted installs of kf5-baloo-file-5.20.0-1.fc24.x86_64 and kde-l10n-sr-15.12.3-3.fc24.noarch
エラーの要約 -------------
[mfabian@Fedora-Workstation-netinst-x86_6 ~]$
not sure how many similar conflicts are occurring currently in Fedora 24. Already saw 2 different conflicts for 2 different locale packages.

Wow, the -sr tranlations are conflicts galore alright :(
I'll take a look.
